race.description: Go Hire Site Rentals Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: ROMANCASTLE (12) travelled just off the pace then worked home well without threatening on debut over 1000m at this track. Nicely drawn and likely to have more to offer over an extra furlong this afternoon. PAZYRYK (11) has been just behind the placegetters at both runs this prep. Lightly raced filly who may go to a new level this afternoon with the winkers going on. LADY OF THE CASTLE (7) disappointed in town last time but her excellent effort on debut suggests she has a lot more under the bonnet. RACH (2) only went down narrowly first up at Canterbury and has to be included off the back of that effort, especially with the aid of the claim.
